nues (KEDB)<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\r\n  normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\"> Des vues\r\n  diffrentes des donnes pour les agents et les utilisateurs<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\r\n  normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\"> Une recherche\r\n  par mots-cls vocateurs bass sur la description de l\'incident<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;\r\n  margin-bottom:0cm;margin-left:54.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;mso-add-space:\r\n  auto;text-align:justify;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;\r\n  margin-bottom:0cm;margin-left:54.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;mso-add-space:\r\n  auto;text-align:justify;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;\r\n  margin-bottom:0cm;margin-left:54.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;mso-add-space:\r\n  auto;text-align:justify;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;\r\n  margin-bottom:0cm;margin-left:54.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;mso-add-space:\r\n  auto;text-align:justify;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;\r\n  margin-bottom:0cm;margin-left:54.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;mso-add-space:\r\n  auto;text-align:justify;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;\r\n  margin-bottom:0cm;margin-left:54.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;mso-add-space:\r\n  auto;text-align:justify;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:normal;mso-list:l6 level1 lfo6\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\n  background:lime;mso-highlight:lime\">3.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;background:lime;mso-highlight:\r\n  lime\">Libre-service pour l\'utilisateur final<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\n  justify;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Les\r\n  capacits de support libre-service permettent aux utilisateurs de rsoudre\r\n  leurs problmes plus rapidement, sans avoir  attendre un agent. <o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\n  justify;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Certaines\r\n  des fonctionnalits libre-service les plus courantes comprennent :<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\n  justify;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">\r\n  La recherche dans la base de connaissances<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\n  justify;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">\r\n  Les diagnostics en libre-service<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\n  justify;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">\r\n  Les processus courants automatiss<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\n  justify;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">\r\n  Le formulaire de demande de service<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n  0cm;margin-left:54.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;mso-add-space:auto;text-align:\r\n  justify;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:normal;mso-list:l6 level1 lfo6\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\n  background:lime;mso-highlight:lime\">4.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;background:lime;mso-highlight:\r\n  lime\">Gestion du centre de services et reporting<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\n  justify;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Les\r\n  fonctions de gestion et de reporting sont essentielles au sein du centre de\r\n  services lorsque les chefs de service cherchent  optimiser les cots\r\n  oprationnels, identifier au pralable les problmes impactant l\'entreprise\r\n  (incidents majeurs), grer la satisfaction client et garantir le respect des\r\n  SLA. La technologie peut jouer un rle important dans les fonctions de\r\n  gestion en permettant aux responsables du centre de services d\'avoir une vue\r\n  d\'ensemble de leurs oprations et des donnes ncessaires pour prendre des\r\n  dcisions claires. Certaines des capacits principales de gestion et de\r\n  reporting du centre de services sont :<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\n  justify;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">\r\n  Les capacits de gestion des <span style=\"background:lime;mso-highlight:lime\">incidents</span>\r\n  majeurs<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\n  justify;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">\r\n  Les tableaux de bord pour la <span style=\"background:lime;mso-highlight:lime\">performance</span>\r\n  et la disponibilit des services<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\n  justify;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">\r\n  Les <span style=\"background:lime;mso-highlight:lime\">rapports</span> de\r\n  mesure sur les agents/la gestion des appels<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\n  justify;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">\r\n  Les rapports sur le respect des <span style=\"background:lime;mso-highlight:\r\n  lime\">SLA</span><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\n  justify;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">\r\n  Les <span style=\"background:lime;mso-highlight:lime\">analyses</span> des\r\n  problmes connus<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n  <td width=\"986\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:369.7pt;border-top:none;border-left:\r\n  none;border-bottom:solid windowtext 1.0pt;border-right:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\r\n  mso-border-top-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;mso-border-left-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;\r\n  mso-border-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;height:698.3pt\">\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;\r\n  text-align:center;line-height:normal\"><u><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">III.\r\n  La Gestion Des Services Informatiques (ITSM)<o:p></o:p></span></u></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;\r\n  text-align:center;line-height:normal\"><u><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&nbsp;</span></u></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;\r\n  text-align:center;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;mso-add-space:\r\n  auto;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;background:#8EAADB;mso-background-themecolor:\r\n  accent1;mso-background-themetint:153\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Dfinition<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\r\n  normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">ITSM signifie\r\n  Information Technology Service Management. L\'ITSM permet de voir son systme\r\n  d\'information comme un service pour ses clients finaux et d\'en dgager une\r\n  valeur. Les logiciels d\'ITSM sont des logiciels informatiques conus pour\r\n  grer tous les services informatiques de l\'entreprise<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;mso-add-space:\r\n  auto;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;background:#8EAADB;mso-background-themecolor:\r\n  accent1;mso-background-themetint:153\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Pourquoi\r\n  mettre en place une gestion ITSM ?<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\n  justify;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">L\'implmentation\r\n  d\'une gestion ITSM efficace permet de fournir des services informatiques de\r\n  meilleure qualit  ses clients internes et externes, plus rapidement et avec\r\n  des cots maitriss. <o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;mso-add-space:\r\n  auto;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;background:#8EAADB;mso-background-themecolor:\r\n  accent1;mso-background-themetint:153\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Ce\r\n  quoi un ITSM ?<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\n  justify;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Aujourdhui,\r\n  quelle que soit leur taille, les entreprises sont dpendantes de la\r\n  technologie et doivent dune faon ou dune autre interagir avec les services\r\n  informatiques. De plus en plus sollicits, ces services font face  des\r\n  problmes rcurrents : <span style=\"background:yellow;mso-highlight:yellow\">manque\r\n  dun management</span> et <span style=\"background:yellow;mso-highlight:yellow\">dune\r\n  visibilit globale des infrastructures</span>, <span style=\"background:yellow;\r\n  mso-highlight:yellow\">incidents mal qualifis</span>, <span style=\"background:\r\n  yellow;mso-highlight:yellow\">multitudes doutils sans centralisation</span>, <span style=\"background:yellow;mso-highlight:yellow\">gestion de multiples\r\n  configurations des outils,</span> etc. La complexit du rle fait apparatre\r\n  des dysfonctionnements qui rendent les services peu efficients, augmentent\r\n  les cots et dgradent la satisfaction.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\n  justify;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\n  justify;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Lun\r\n  des rles cls de lapproche ITSM est daider les dpartements en charge des\r\n  infrastructures  simplifier leurs tches en rduisant la complexit des\r\n  architectures informatiques et en unifiant les relations de travail entre\r\n  quipes informatiques et utilisateurs finaux.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;mso-add-space:\r\n  auto;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;background:#8EAADB;mso-background-themecolor:\r\n  accent1;mso-background-themetint:153\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Contexte\r\n  et bnfice attendus<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\n  justify;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">\r\n  Les entreprises sont de plus en plus dpendantes de leurs services\r\n  informatiques pour dvelopper et maintenir un avantage concurrentiel sur leur\r\n  march.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\n  justify;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">\r\n  L\'objectif du dpartement informatique est de fournir, sous la pression les\r\n  services adapts aux besoins <span style=\"background:yellow;mso-highlight:\r\n  yellow\">d\'aujourd\'hui</span> et d\'anticiper ceux de <span style=\"background:\r\n  yellow;mso-highlight:yellow\">demain</span>.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n  .0001pt;mso-add-space:auto;text-align:justify;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;\r\n  mso-add-space:auto;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;background:#8EAADB;\r\n  mso-background-themecolor:accent1;mso-background-themetint:153\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Intgration du CSI dans le ITSM<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\r\n  normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Le centre de\r\n  services informatiques fonctionne comme un lment des oprations de gestion\r\n  de service au sens large. Mme si le centre de services informatiques peut\r\n  fonctionner de faon indpendante, la performance et la valeur seront\r\n  augmentes en intgrant le logiciel du centre de services avec d\'autres\r\n  parties du systme ITSM de l\'entreprise. Certaines des intgrations les plus\r\n  intressantes comprennent :<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n  .0001pt;mso-add-space:auto;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">1.\r\n  La base de donnes de la gestion de la configuration (CMDB)<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n  .0001pt;mso-add-space:auto;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">2.\r\n  La gestion des changements<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n  .0001pt;mso-add-space:auto;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">3.\r\n  La surveillance<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n  .0001pt;mso-add-space:auto;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">4.\r\n  La gestion des problmes<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n  .0001pt;mso-add-space:auto;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">5.\r\n  La gestion des actifs<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\r\n  normal;background:#D9E2F3;mso-background-themecolor:accent1;mso-background-themetint:\r\n  51\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">La base de donnes de\r\n  la gestion de la configuration (CMDB)<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\r\n  normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\"> Donnant aux\r\n  agents laccs au rseau complexe des interdpendances techniques et aux\r\n  informations des composants de configuration pour leur permettre de mieux\r\n  valuer les impacts des incidents<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\r\n  normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">La gestion des\r\n  changements<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\r\n  normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\"> Un grand nombre\r\n  de problmes technologiques sont causs par des changements planifis. En\r\n  donnant aux agents accs au systme de gestion des changements, ils seront\r\n  capables d\'identifier les incidents associs plus rapidement<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\r\n  normal;background:#D9E2F3;mso-background-themecolor:accent1;mso-background-themetint:\r\n  51\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">La surveillance<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\r\n  normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\"> Les\r\n  surveillants de service et d\'infrastructure donnent une visibilit en temps\r\n  rel sur la sant de l\'environnement informatique et donnent lalerte lorsque\r\n  quelque chose ne va pas. En intgrant les capacits de surveillance avec le\r\n  systme du centre de services, beaucoup d\'incidents peuvent tre identifis\r\n  sans que lutilisateur nait besoin d\'appeler et de signaler un problme<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\r\n  normal;background:#D9E2F3;mso-background-themecolor:accent1;mso-background-themetint:\r\n  51\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">La gestion des\r\n  problmes<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\r\n  normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\"> Le meilleur\r\n  moyen de grer les incidents est d\'viter qu\'ils se produisent. Intgrer les\r\n  capacits de gestion des problmes permet non seulement d\'aider les agents du\r\n  centre de services de comprendre quels problmes connus sont dj en train\r\n  d\'tre traits, mais permet aussi aux quipes de gestion des problmes de se\r\n  concentrer sur ceux qui causent le plus grand nombre d\'incidents.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\r\n  normal;background:#D9E2F3;mso-background-themecolor:accent1;mso-background-themetint:\r\n  51\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">La gestion des actifs<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\r\n  normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\"> Les\r\n  interactions du centre de services avec les utilisateurs sont un moment idal\r\n  pour vrifier et mettre  jour les informations de gestion des actifs. Donner\r\n  aux agents la possibilit de voir et de mettre  jour les donnes de gestion\r\n  des actifs peut tre un moyen efficace d\'amliorer la qualit de cet ensemble\r\n  de donnes importantes de l\'ITSM.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\r\n  normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;\r\n  text-align:center;line-height:normal;background:#D9E2F3;mso-background-themecolor:\r\n  accent1;mso-background-themetint:51\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">CONCLUSION<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\n  justify;line-height:normal;background:yellow\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Le\r\n  centre de services informatiques est un lment essentiel de la fonction ITSM\r\n  des entreprises modernes. A mesure que le rle de la technologie en tant que\r\n  partie intgrante des processus commerciaux et des expriences utilisateurs\r\n  slargit, il est essentiel de s\'assurer que les services technologiques\r\n  fonctionnent correctement.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\n  justify;line-height:normal;background:yellow\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Le\r\n  centre de services informatiques centr sur l\'utilisateur, avec ses workflows\r\n  bien dfinis, sa richesse de connaissances sur l\'organisation et ses\r\n  connexions avec le reste de l\'organisation informatique est le lien critique\r\n  entre les utilisateurs et l\'organisation informatique.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\n  justify;line-height:normal;background:yellow\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Chaque\r\n  organisation est unique et votre centre de services, ainsi que les outils que\r\n  vous utilisez, doivent tre totalement en phase avec les besoins de votre\r\n  entreprise. Que votre organisation soit davantage centre sur la technologie\r\n  et ait besoin d\'une solution ITSM intgre, ou quelle ait une vue plus large\r\n  du centre de services en prenant en charge non seulement lIT mais d\'autres\r\n  fonctions business qui utilisent un systme de gestion du centre de services\r\n  clients.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n </tr>\r\n</tbody></table><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&nbsp;</span></p>',	5,	'0000-00-00 00:00:00',	1),
(287,	108,	'BLABLABLA',	'<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; background: rgb(247, 202, 172);\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 17.12px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">GESTION DUN CENTRE INFORMATIQUE</span><u><o:p></o:p></u></span></p><table class=\"MsoTableGrid\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" width=\"1999\" style=\"width: 749.6pt; border: none;\"><tbody><tr><td width=\"1999\" colspan=\"2\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding: 0cm 5.4pt; width: 749.6pt; border: 1pt solid windowtext;\"><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: center; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\"><u><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Notion de centre informatique (CI)<o:p></o:p></span></u></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background: rgb(142, 170, 219);\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",=\"\" \"serif\";=\"\" background-image:=\"\" initial;=\"\" background-position:=\"\" background-size:=\"\" background-repeat:=\"\" background-attachment:=\"\" background-origin:=\"\" background-clip:=\"\" initial;\"=\"\">Dfinition</span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\"><u><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">Un CI:</span></u></span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">est un centre de traitement de donnes, un bureau ou un service responsable du traitement systmatique des donnes et de linformation.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">Le traitement est effectu  laide dordinateurs quips du matriel et des logiciels ncessaires pour accomplir cette tche. Ces ordinateurs sont gnralement mis en rseau et disposent dune connexion Internet.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background: rgb(142, 170, 219);\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",=\"\" \"serif\";=\"\" background-image:=\"\" initial;=\"\" background-position:=\"\" background-size:=\"\" background-repeat:=\"\" background-attachment:=\"\" background-origin:=\"\" background-clip:=\"\" initial;\"=\"\">Mission</span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\"><u><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">Un CI</span></u></span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">est charge de la conception, limplmentation et mais aussi la formation des utilisateurs, la maintenance du matriel informatique et le dveloppement dtudes de faisabilit font partie de ses missions.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background: rgb(142, 170, 219);\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",=\"\" \"serif\";=\"\" background-image:=\"\" initial;=\"\" background-position:=\"\" background-size:=\"\" background-repeat:=\"\" background-attachment:=\"\" background-origin:=\"\" background-clip:=\"\" initial;\"=\"\">Centre informatique : o et quand<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">Centre de dpouillement: il fonction comme un grand type de systme informatique.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background: rgb(142, 170, 219);\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">Les quatre activits principales de ce type de systme:<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt 14.2pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; color: rgb(47, 84, 150);\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal;\"></span></span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\";=\"\" color:#2f5496;mso-themecolor:accent1;mso-themeshade:191\"=\"\">La saisie des donnes (saisie des donnes dans le systme),<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt 14.2pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; color: rgb(47, 84, 150);\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal;\"></span></span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\";=\"\" color:#2f5496;mso-themecolor:accent1;mso-themeshade:191\"=\"\">Le stockage des donnes (gnralement sur les serveurs),<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt 14.2pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; color: rgb(47, 84, 150);\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal;\"></span></span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\";=\"\" color:#2f5496;mso-themecolor:accent1;mso-themeshade:191\"=\"\">Le traitement (somme des votes, estimation des pourcentages, et<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt 14.2pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: Symbol;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal;\"></span></span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\";=\"\" color:#2f5496;mso-themecolor:accent1;mso-themeshade:191\"=\"\">Sauvegarde des informations.</span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background: rgb(142, 170, 219);\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">Caractristique (Etude pralable gographique)<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">Lune des principales caractristiques de ces tablissements est la prservation des quipements au niveau physique. Tout dabord:<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\";mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\"\"=\"\">1.<span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal;\"></span></span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\";=\"\" color:#c45911;mso-themecolor:accent2;mso-themeshade:191\"=\"\">Une localisation gographique</span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">doit tre choisie en tenant compte des diffrents points. Combien coute le terrain, le taxes, le redevance ou location, historique des catastrophes naturelles et la qualit de la communication.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt 14.2pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">2.<span style=\"color: rgb(196, 89, 17);\">Gestion de temprature:</span>Climatiseur, orientation du btiment contre le rayon solaire.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt 14.2pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\"></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt 14.2pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\"></span></p></td></tr><tr style=\"height: 698.3pt;\"><td width=\"1013\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding: 0cm 5.4pt; width: 379.9pt; border-right: 1pt solid windowtext; border-bottom: 1pt solid windowtext; border-left: 1pt solid windowtext; border-image: initial; border-top: none; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; height: 698.3pt;\"><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: center; line-height: normal;\"><u><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">II. Le Centre De Service Informatique<o:p></o:p></span></u></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: center; line-height: normal;\"><u><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">Rfrenc Avec ITIL<span style=\"color: red;\">p9</span><o:p></o:p></span></u></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\"></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background: rgb(142, 170, 219);\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">Dfinition<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal;\">Le premier point de contact entre les utilisateurs et une organisation IT.<span style=\"font-weight: 700;\"><u>Selon ITIL,</u></span>le centre de services est le point de contact unique (SPOC : Single Point of Contact) entre le prestataire de services (IT) et les utilisateurs pour les activits quotidiennes. Un centre classique gre les incidents et les demandes des services mais a traitant les communications des utilisateurs concernant les pannes ou les modifications dans le service.<span style=\"color: rgb(196, 89, 17);\">Il couvre un large ventail et est pour fournir  l\'utilisateur un guichet unique pour tous leurs besoins informatiques. Ainsi, le centre de services joue<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal;\">Rle: Faciliter l\'intgration des processus<span style=\"background: yellow;\">business</span>avec<span style=\"background: yellow;\">l\'cosystme technologique</span>et<span style=\"background: yellow;\">l\'infrastructure largie de la gestion de services</span>.<span style=\"color: rgb(196, 89, 17);\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background: rgb(142, 170, 219);\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">Origine et volution dans la Gestion des Services Informatiques (ITSM)<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">La fonction du<span style=\"color: red;\">support client</span>est ne  la fin des annes 80 afin daider  rgler les problmes. Ils ne possdaient pas de SLA, ni dobjectifs bass sur le temps pour rgler les problmes.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">ITIL est apparu dans les annes 90, recensant les meilleures pratiques de la gestion des services informatiques, que le concept du centre de services informatiques centr sur l\'utilisateur a commenc  merger.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background: rgb(142, 170, 219);\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">Centre de Service informatique : Support Client et Centre dAppel<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\";=\"\" color:#538135;mso-themecolor:accent6;mso-themeshade:191\"=\"\">Le Support client:</span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\";=\"\" color:#385623;mso-themecolor:accent6;mso-themeshade:128\"=\"\"></span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">Est une ressource conue pour fournir au client ou  l\'utilisateur interne des renseignements et du support associs aux processus, produits et services de l\'entreprise.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">Canaux: Site physique, web, messagerie instantanes ou mail.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\