"\">Alerte prcoce</span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">&nbsp;des problmes potentiels<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt 21.3pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background: rgb(142, 170, 219);\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">Les meilleures pratiques du centre de services informatiques<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">Les entreprises oprent avec des centres de services informatiques depuis de nombreuses annes, ce qui a permis didentifier les meilleures pratiques.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt 54pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\";mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\"\"=\"\">1.<span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\";=\"\" background:red;mso-highlight:red\"=\"\">Lengagement par rapport aux clients</span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: Wingdings;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-varia