e-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\"> Une recherche par mots-cls vocateurs bass sur la description de l\'incident<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt 54pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt 54pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt 54pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><img src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" data-filename=\"R.png\" style=\"width: 934.133px; height: 467.066px;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt 54pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt 54pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt 54pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\";mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";=\"\" background:lime;mso-highlight:lime\"=\"\">3.<span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\";background:lime;mso-highlight:=\"\" lime\"=\"\">Libre-service pour l\'utilisateur final<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">Les capacits de support libre-service permettent aux utilisateurs de rsoudre leurs problmes plus rapidement, sans avoir  attendre un agent.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">Certaines des fonctionnalits libre-service les plus courantes comprennent :<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\"> La recherche dans la base de connaissances<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\"> Les diagnostics en libre-service<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\"> Les processus courants automatiss<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\"> Le formulaire de demande de service<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt 54pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\";mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";=\"\" background:lime;mso-highlight:lime\"=\"\">4.<span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\";background:lime;mso-highlight:=\"\" lime\"=\"\">Gestion du centre de services et reporting<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\">Les fonctions de gestion et de reporting sont essentielles au sein du centre de services lorsque les chefs de service cherchent  optimiser les cots oprationnels, identifier au pralable les problmes impactant l\'entreprise (incidents majeurs), grer la satisfaction client et garantir le respect des SLA. La technologie peut jouer un rle important dans les fonctions de gestion en permettant aux responsables du centre de services d\'avoir une vue d\'ensemble de leurs oprations et des donnes ncessaires pour prendre des dcisions claires. Certaines des capacits principales de gestion et de reporting du centre de services sont :<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\"> Les capacits de gestion des&nbsp;<span style=\"background: lime;\">incidents</span>&nbsp;majeurs<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\"> Les tableaux de bord pour la&nbsp;<span style=\"background: lime;\">performance</span>&nbsp;et la disponibilit des services<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\"> Les&nbsp;<span style=\"background: lime;\">rapports</span>&nbsp;de mesure sur les agents/la gestion des appels<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\